import React from 'react'
import { Card, Button, Row, Form, Typography } from 'antd'
// import ExistingData from './ExistingData'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { APP_PREFIX_PATH } from 'configs/AppConfig'
import FileUploadForm from './FileUploadForm'
import FormOptions from './FormOptions'
import { StyledButton, StyledNavButton } from 'constants/StyledComponents'
import { CloudUploadOutlined, ToTopOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons'

const { Title } = Typography

function OpsAdmin(props) {
    console.log(props)
    return (
        <Card>
            <Card>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Item justify="center" style={{ textAlign: 'center', marginTop: '2.5%' }}>
                        <Title level={1}>Upload Transactions</Title>
                    </Form.Item>
                    <Row style={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center'}}>
                        {/* <StyledNavButton style={{ marginRight: '3%'}}><LeftCircleOutlined style={{ marginRight: '2%' }} />Go to recommendations</StyledNavButton> */}
                        <Link to={`${APP_PREFIX_PATH}/journeys/journey-ivr/transaction`}>
                            <StyledNavButton style={{ marginRight: '3%'}}><ToTopOutlined style={{ marginRight: '4%' }} />Add a single transaction</StyledNavButton>
                        </Link>
                        <Link to={`${APP_PREFIX_PATH}/journeys/journey-ivr/transaction`}>
                            <StyledNavButton style={{ marginLeft: '3%'}}>Upload an entire file<CloudUploadOutlined style={{ marginLeft: '2%' }} /></StyledNavButton>
                        </Link>
                    </Row>
                    {/* <FileUploadForm esData={ props.esData } />
                    <FormOptions /> */}
                </Form>
            </Card>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default OpsAdmin
